-- MATH-06: Quaternion methods (24 of 24 functions, raymath.h lines
-- 1731-2170). Raymath 5.5 exposes exactly 24 Quaternion RMAPI functions
-- (verified via `grep -cE '^RMAPI [A-Za-z0-9_]+ Quaternion[A-Z]' raymath.h`).
-- Plan text claimed 26 pre-emptively вЂ” resolved GREEN at 24.
--
-- Same 16 B struct-by-value in/out template as Vector4 (Quaternion is
-- layout-identical to Vector4 via Phase 60-02 _Static_assert).
-- QuaternionEquals returns int в†’ shim coerces to Bool (matches
-- Vector2/3/4 Equals pattern). Cross-type: QuaternionFromMatrix takes
-- Matrix (64 B) in; QuaternionToMatrix returns Matrix (64 B) out;
-- QuaternionTransform takes Matrix as second arg; QuaternionToEuler
-- returns Vector3; QuaternionFromVector3ToVector3 takes 2 Vector3s.
-- QuaternionToAxisAngle is the 2-tuple out-param case в†’ declared above
-- alongside Matrix.decompose as a tuple return.
